# Health Monitoring System Implementation Plan

## Goal Description
Implement an end-to-end Health Monitoring System that ingests raw patient vitals from multiple sources, processes them through an Intelligence Layer for feature engineering and ML-based risk prediction, and presents the decision along with explainability via a Streamlit Dashboard.

## Proposed Changes

### Configuration
